					<p><strong>The skill and experience you need to have:</strong></p>

					<ul class="normal-list">
						<li>Advanced Adobe Photoshop and/or Illustrator skills</li>
						<li>Basic understanding and practical experience with some of the following HTML/CSS, or JavaScript</li>
						<li>Education/experience in Design, UI/UX</li>
						<li>Experience designing user functional elements or learning material</li>
						<li>Experience working as a contractor or on cross-functional teams</li>
